317
00:24:04,010 --> 00:24:06,090
Oh my goodness.

318
00:24:06,170 --> 00:24:07,910
What are we to do?

319
00:24:08,810 --> 00:24:10,610
Mother, I'm sorry.

320
00:24:11,750 --> 00:24:13,690
