00:35:29,910 --> 00:35:30,910
Yes.

492
00:35:31,990 --> 00:35:34,740
Divide what's left of Anchovy's share among the others.

493
00:35:35,070 --> 00:35:36,070
Yes.

494
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:40,950
Pollack, Loach, go get the rice.

495
00:35:41,970 --> 00:35:43,310
