00:36:28,350 --> 00:36:30,450
Have you ever heard of a drifting water weed?

514
00:36:30,490 --> 00:36:32,340
Oh, please don't use difficult words.

515
00:36:32,610 --> 00:36:34,490
We don't understand difficult things.

516
00:36:34,730 --> 00:36:36,280
