517
00:36:36,430 --> 00:36:37,530
Ah, this is annoying.

518
00:36:37,850 --> 00:36:38,310
Sigh.

519
00:36:38,570 --> 00:36:39,570
Oh, how annoying.

520
00:36:40,230 --> 00:36:43,030
Today Daejeon, tomorrow Gyeongseong.

521
00:36:43,530 --> 00:36:46,980
The loneliness of this drifting water weed, wandering here and there.

522
00:36:50,370 --> 00:36:51,470
